## 2. Degradation Prediction Model

The model uses a hybrid approach combining reliability engineering (Weibull distribution for failure analysis) and machine learning (LSTM neural network for time-series forecasting) to predict degradation curves. It processes historical failure data and real-time sensor readings to forecast component health over time.

